WEBVTT

00:01:35.790 --> 00:01:41.070 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:01:41.180 --> 00:01:43.750 line:80%
[Episode 6]

00:01:43.820 --> 00:01:47.059 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:01:57.390 --> 00:01:59.029 line:80%
Zheng! Zheng!

00:01:59.330 --> 00:02:00.820 line:80%
My sister is going to butcher  a pig.

00:02:00.820 --> 00:02:02.260 line:80%
Come and watch.

00:02:02.670 --> 00:02:03.610 line:80%
Butcher a pig?

00:02:09.430 --> 00:02:12.020 line:80%
Don't move. I'll make it quick.

00:02:12.180 --> 00:02:13.750 line:80%
You've been a good pig in this life.

00:02:13.750 --> 00:02:15.550 line:80%
Be a good person in the next life!

00:02:16.550 --> 00:02:18.790 line:80%
I feel like I've heard that somewhere.

00:02:19.810 --> 00:02:21.629 line:80%
My sister is amazing, isn't she?

00:02:31.550 --> 00:02:32.200 line:80%
Yan Zheng,

00:02:32.760 --> 00:02:34.360 line:80%
take Changning inside.

00:02:34.430 --> 00:02:35.690 line:80%
Don't let her see this.

00:02:35.940 --> 00:02:37.940 line:80%
Or she'll have nightmares tonight.

00:02:38.640 --> 00:02:39.200 line:80%
Okay.

00:02:40.160 --> 00:02:40.920 line:80%
Let's go.

00:03:02.200 --> 00:03:03.060 line:80%
Don't look.

00:03:08.160 --> 00:03:09.360 line:80%
Don't be scared.

00:03:11.480 --> 00:03:12.920 line:80%
I'm not scared of butchering pigs.

00:03:12.920 --> 00:03:15.080 line:80%
I meant don't be scared of my sister.

00:03:40.040 --> 00:03:41.040 line:80%
Do you need a hand?

00:03:46.820 --> 00:03:49.750 line:80%
Did I scare you just now?

00:03:51.950 --> 00:03:54.000 line:80%
If you were scared or disgusted,

00:03:54.200 --> 00:03:55.090 line:80%
just say so.

00:03:55.160 --> 00:03:56.080 line:80%
I'm used to it.

00:03:59.830 --> 00:04:01.100 line:80%
I wasn't scared.

00:04:03.020 --> 00:04:04.420 line:80%
Then you were disgusted.

00:04:11.220 --> 00:04:12.840 line:80%
You didn't mind my injury.

00:04:13.550 --> 00:04:15.610 line:80%
Why would I mind that you're capable?

00:04:30.100 --> 00:04:31.760 line:80%
Stop looking. Go back inside.

00:04:35.560 --> 00:04:37.140 line:80%
You should go inside and rest too.

00:04:37.140 --> 00:04:37.959 line:80%
Stop adding wood.

00:04:37.959 --> 00:04:40.400 line:80%
When scalding the pig bristles,
it smells terrible.

00:04:40.400 --> 00:04:41.720 line:80%
This is nothing.

00:04:41.720 --> 00:04:43.520 line:80%
I've smelled worse things.

00:04:43.790 --> 00:04:44.990 line:80%
Like burning bodies.

00:04:47.800 --> 00:04:48.600 line:80%
Right.

00:04:49.230 --> 00:04:50.630 line:80%
You were an armed escort.

00:04:51.310 --> 00:04:53.040 line:80%
You must have seen dead people.

00:05:32.709 --> 00:05:33.870 line:80%
This pork—

00:05:33.959 --> 00:05:35.820 line:80%
do you want me to hang it up for you?

00:05:36.310 --> 00:05:37.540 line:80%
Hang on a second.

00:05:38.630 --> 00:05:39.670 line:80%
This pork

00:05:39.920 --> 00:05:40.980 line:80%
needs to be salted.

00:05:41.670 --> 00:05:42.360 line:80%
Like this.

00:05:42.380 --> 00:05:44.650 line:80%
Spread the salt evenly over the meat,

00:05:44.800 --> 00:05:47.060 line:80%
let it cure for a few days,
then hang it up.

00:05:54.280 --> 00:05:54.940 line:80%
Let me do it.

00:05:55.870 --> 00:05:56.670 line:80%
I'll help you.

00:06:13.170 --> 00:06:15.670 line:80%
My father and mother
used to make cured meat like this.

00:06:15.670 --> 00:06:17.000 line:80%
They helped each other.

00:06:17.340 --> 00:06:18.480 line:80%
Then what did you do?

00:06:19.740 --> 00:06:22.340 line:80%
Changning and I
would make trouble on the side.

00:06:31.520 --> 00:06:34.150 line:80%
This piece of pork is a bit too big.

00:06:34.310 --> 00:06:36.310 line:80%
I need to make a few cuts
for the flavor to soak in.

00:06:36.310 --> 00:06:37.720 line:80%
Pass me the knife.

00:07:04.400 --> 00:07:04.960 line:80%
This one.

00:07:07.750 --> 00:07:08.720 line:80%
This knife...

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:10.620 line:80%
where did it come from?

00:07:11.310 --> 00:07:12.970 line:80%
My father had someone make it.

00:07:13.560 --> 00:07:16.290 line:80%
Do you know what this knife is made of?

00:07:16.840 --> 00:07:17.840 line:80%
Iron, obviously.

00:07:18.670 --> 00:07:20.330 line:80%
What else could it be? Silver?

00:07:21.130 --> 00:07:22.330 line:80%
But Father said that

00:07:23.230 --> 00:07:25.620 line:80%
these two knives are our family heirlooms.

00:07:25.620 --> 00:07:27.480 line:80%
They supported our whole family.

00:07:31.850 --> 00:07:33.709 line:80%
Your father must have been quite skilled
in martial arts.

00:07:33.709 --> 00:07:35.040 line:80%
Where did he learn that?

00:07:35.230 --> 00:07:37.550 line:80%
He traveled extensively when he was young.

00:07:37.550 --> 00:07:39.870 line:80%
Maybe he met some reclusive master.

00:08:18.160 --> 00:08:18.890 line:80%
You won.

00:08:20.340 --> 00:08:22.020 line:80%
Uncle, I won!

00:08:29.560 --> 00:08:31.070 line:80%
You gained a slight advantage.

00:08:31.070 --> 00:08:33.219 line:80%
Is it worth getting so excited?

00:08:33.640 --> 00:08:35.209 line:80%
General He

00:08:35.229 --> 00:08:36.540 line:80%
was just teasing you.

00:08:45.030 --> 00:08:45.580 line:80%
This...

00:08:48.640 --> 00:08:50.430 line:80%
This salt is very expensive.

00:08:51.310 --> 00:08:53.430 line:80%
Why be stingy over a little salt?

00:08:54.950 --> 00:08:57.750 line:80%
You don't run the house,
so you don't know the cost.

00:09:02.590 --> 00:09:04.880 line:80%
Changyu, is the pig tail ready?

00:09:06.960 --> 00:09:09.410 line:80%
I just put it in the pot.
It needs a while.

00:09:09.550 --> 00:09:10.160 line:80%
Look.

00:09:12.780 --> 00:09:14.040 line:80%
It's still early,

00:09:14.190 --> 00:09:15.920 line:80%
and you're already craving it?

00:09:16.070 --> 00:09:17.000 line:80%
Little glutton.

00:09:17.640 --> 00:09:18.830 line:80%
I'm not a little glutton.

00:09:18.830 --> 00:09:20.100 line:80%
Yes, you are.

00:09:24.040 --> 00:09:24.770 line:80%
We caught it!

00:09:48.520 --> 00:09:49.580 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:09:50.290 --> 00:09:52.670 line:80%
I've seen this gyrfalcon
near our place several times.

00:09:52.670 --> 00:09:53.750 line:80%
So I set a trap.

00:09:53.920 --> 00:09:55.980 line:80%
I didn't expect to actually catch it.

00:09:58.890 --> 00:10:00.820 line:80%
Little beast, you dared to bite me!

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:03.350 line:80%
I'll take you to the market tomorrow

00:10:03.350 --> 00:10:04.640 line:80%
and sell you for ten taels of silver.

00:10:04.640 --> 00:10:05.710 line:80%
At the market,

00:10:05.990 --> 00:10:08.120 line:80%
few people buy live animals like this.

00:10:08.470 --> 00:10:09.760 line:80%
Ordinary families can't tame them.

00:10:09.760 --> 00:10:11.710 line:80%
These things are wild by nature

00:10:11.880 --> 00:10:13.210 line:80%
and easily hurt people.

00:10:13.520 --> 00:10:14.920 line:80%
That's a shame.

00:10:15.240 --> 00:10:16.550 line:80%
Its wing is hurt too.

00:10:17.850 --> 00:10:18.850 line:80%
How about...

00:10:19.120 --> 00:10:20.360 line:80%
we just kill it

00:10:20.400 --> 00:10:21.860 line:80%
and make some soup with it?

00:10:21.880 --> 00:10:23.280 line:80%
Changning, turn around.

00:10:23.530 --> 00:10:24.420 line:80%
No!

00:10:28.070 --> 00:10:29.070 line:80%
I once...

00:10:29.800 --> 00:10:31.730 line:80%
ate this kind of gyrfalcon's meat.

00:10:31.880 --> 00:10:34.190 line:80%
It was tough and sour. Inedible.

00:10:35.840 --> 00:10:38.010 line:80%
Don't worry. I'll cook it.

00:10:38.060 --> 00:10:40.500 line:80%
Our brine could make a block of wood
taste good.

00:10:40.500 --> 00:10:41.270 line:80%
No.

00:10:46.310 --> 00:10:49.350 line:80%
Actually,
I know a little about taming birds.

00:10:49.590 --> 00:10:50.920 line:80%
I can try to tame it.

00:10:51.390 --> 00:10:54.110 line:80%
A tamed gyrfalcon
can sell for over 100 taels.

00:10:56.180 --> 00:10:57.460 line:80%
Over 100 taels?

00:11:01.170 --> 00:11:02.730 line:80%
That's worth way too much.

00:11:03.280 --> 00:11:04.550 line:80%
Changning, get a chicken coop.

00:11:04.550 --> 00:11:05.310 line:80%
Okay.

00:11:06.710 --> 00:11:08.570 line:80%
Then I'll keep you at home for now,

00:11:08.750 --> 00:11:10.010 line:80%
Little Hundred Taels.

00:11:18.350 --> 00:11:19.310 line:80%
Stupid thing.

00:11:37.550 --> 00:11:38.610 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:11:40.640 --> 00:11:42.040 line:80%
I'm bandaging its wound.

00:11:42.880 --> 00:11:44.550 line:80%
Why are you using this?

00:11:47.330 --> 00:11:49.580 line:80%
What's wrong with using this cloth?

00:11:50.400 --> 00:11:52.260 line:80%
This is the hair ribbon I gave you.

00:11:56.690 --> 00:11:58.750 line:80%
I thought it was just a piece of cloth.

00:12:08.070 --> 00:12:10.320 line:80%
Father, Mother, the year is ending.

00:12:11.470 --> 00:12:13.010 line:80%
This is the New Year pig.

00:12:13.040 --> 00:12:14.250 line:80%
Have a taste.

00:12:18.560 --> 00:12:21.020 line:80%
Today is also the 3rd day
since I got married.

00:12:21.880 --> 00:12:23.040 line:80%
My husband...

00:12:23.350 --> 00:12:26.120 line:80%
He doesn't know
that salt should be used sparingly.

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:27.920 line:80%
But he helped me make cured meat.

00:12:28.630 --> 00:12:30.630 line:80%
And he'd step forward to protect me.

00:12:33.950 --> 00:12:35.670 line:80%
If your spirits are watching,

00:12:36.640 --> 00:12:39.530 line:80%
please bless him with a quick recovery,

00:12:39.670 --> 00:12:40.800 line:80%
and a peaceful life.

00:12:46.460 --> 00:12:47.580 line:80%
As for Song Yan—

00:12:53.170 --> 00:12:54.410 line:80%
that bastard—

00:12:55.240 --> 00:12:56.840 line:80%
make sure he fails the exams.

00:13:04.670 --> 00:13:08.820 line:80%
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

00:13:08.900 --> 00:13:12.820 line:80%
[Tea] [Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:13:12.920 --> 00:13:16.310 line:80%
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop] [Soup Noodles]

00:13:19.460 --> 00:13:24.430 line:80%
[Butcher Shop]

00:13:24.750 --> 00:13:25.740 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:13:38.590 --> 00:13:41.870 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:13:42.400 --> 00:13:45.250 line:80%
Who smashed my stuff?

00:13:45.010 --> 00:13:50.950 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:13:45.670 --> 00:13:48.160 line:80%
Come out and face me if you have the guts!

00:13:48.660 --> 00:13:51.030 line:80%
Hiding makes you a bastard!

00:13:53.280 --> 00:13:54.710 line:80%
What are you looking at me for?

00:13:54.710 --> 00:13:56.440 line:80%
I didn't do it.

00:13:56.880 --> 00:13:58.190 line:80%
This is called...

00:13:58.280 --> 00:14:01.200 line:80%
karma.

00:14:03.800 --> 00:14:05.040 line:80%
Oh no, Changyu.

00:14:05.180 --> 00:14:07.610 line:80%
Your shop was closed for almost 2 months.

00:14:07.800 --> 00:14:09.520 line:80%
Did you forget
to pay the protection money?

00:14:09.460 --> 00:14:13.910 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:14:10.280 --> 00:14:11.940 line:80%
What is the protection money?

00:14:14.070 --> 00:14:17.170 line:80%
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop]

00:14:25.310 --> 00:14:27.240 line:80%
You dare to keep running this shop?

00:14:27.670 --> 00:14:29.190 line:80%
Aren't you afraid of death?

00:14:29.190 --> 00:14:31.590 line:80%
I'd like to see who on this street

00:14:31.930 --> 00:14:33.700 line:80%
dares not pay up.

00:14:35.200 --> 00:14:36.200 line:80%
It's you.

00:14:37.320 --> 00:14:38.400 line:80%
Turn around.

00:14:38.640 --> 00:14:40.280 line:80%
I'm talking to you!

00:14:46.400 --> 00:14:46.980 line:80%
Mrs...

00:14:47.160 --> 00:14:48.370 line:80%
Mrs. Fan.

00:14:53.590 --> 00:14:56.340 line:80%
This butcher shop is yours?

00:14:56.640 --> 00:14:57.280 line:80%
Not bad.

00:14:58.560 --> 00:14:59.690 line:80%
How much do you want?

00:14:59.800 --> 00:15:02.190 line:80%
Misunderstanding.
It's all a misunderstanding.

00:15:02.190 --> 00:15:04.160 line:80%
How could we ask you for protection money?

00:15:04.160 --> 00:15:04.670 line:80%
Hey.

00:15:11.880 --> 00:15:12.550 line:80%
Got it.

00:15:12.550 --> 00:15:13.890 line:80%
Come on. Hurry up and fix it.

00:15:13.890 --> 00:15:15.870 line:80%
[Meat]

00:15:14.120 --> 00:15:15.340 line:80%
Fix it. Fix it.

00:15:18.920 --> 00:15:21.720 line:80%
We're just doing a job we were paid for.

00:15:22.350 --> 00:15:23.520 line:80%
Please don't mind.

00:15:23.520 --> 00:15:24.400 line:80%
Who paid you?

00:15:27.720 --> 00:15:28.760 line:80%
We're fixing your stove.

00:15:28.760 --> 00:15:30.000 line:80%
So please don't ask.

00:15:30.880 --> 00:15:32.090 line:80%
Although we are hooligans,

00:15:32.090 --> 00:15:34.620 line:80%
we know the rule
about not betraying a client.

00:15:35.870 --> 00:15:36.980 line:80%
Very loyal.

00:15:43.110 --> 00:15:45.240 line:80%
The owner of Wang's Braised Meat Shop.

00:15:45.430 --> 00:15:46.190 line:80%
Wang's?

00:15:48.200 --> 00:15:49.860 line:80%
I have no grudge against them.

00:15:49.920 --> 00:15:50.590 line:80%
I swear.

00:15:53.670 --> 00:15:55.800 line:80%
You are... Mr. Jin, right?

00:15:55.800 --> 00:15:56.640 line:80%
I am Jin Yuanbao.

00:15:56.640 --> 00:15:58.900 line:80%
You can call me
Yuanbao or Bao from now on.

00:15:58.990 --> 00:16:01.660 line:80%
[Meat]

00:15:59.240 --> 00:15:59.880 line:80%
Don't just clean up here.

00:15:59.880 --> 00:16:02.010 line:80%
Come on. Clean up inside too. Hurry up.

00:16:03.180 --> 00:16:05.360 line:80%
Mandi, Mancang, Manwu.

00:16:06.190 --> 00:16:07.710 line:80%
You can boss them around however you like.

00:16:07.710 --> 00:16:08.880 line:80%
Are they all surnamed Man?

00:16:08.880 --> 00:16:09.760 line:80%
I named them.

00:16:09.800 --> 00:16:10.920 line:80%
My name is Jin Yuanbao,
which means money, right?

00:16:10.920 --> 00:16:13.120 line:80%
So all their names mean "full of money."

00:16:13.160 --> 00:16:13.950 line:80%
Fix it fast!

00:16:14.170 --> 00:16:15.700 line:80%
I need to open for business.

00:16:15.910 --> 00:16:16.970 line:80%
Open for business?

00:16:17.080 --> 00:16:18.040 line:80%
Open for business?

00:16:18.040 --> 00:16:19.070 line:80%
-You! Come here!
-Come here!

00:16:18.560 --> 00:16:20.450 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:16:19.120 --> 00:16:19.920 line:80%
-Buy meat!
-Come here!

00:16:19.920 --> 00:16:20.640 line:80%
You!

00:16:21.550 --> 00:16:23.840 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:16:22.140 --> 00:16:24.120 line:80%
-I'm talking to you two!
-Come here.

00:16:24.120 --> 00:16:25.180 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:16:25.280 --> 00:16:26.810 line:80%
Forcing people to buy meat?

00:16:29.590 --> 00:16:30.820 line:80%
Buy... Buy...

00:16:31.120 --> 00:16:32.120 line:80%
Buy some pork!

00:16:31.650 --> 00:16:34.620 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:16:32.120 --> 00:16:32.760 line:80%
Don't...

00:16:33.800 --> 00:16:34.690 line:80%
Would you like to buy some?

00:16:34.690 --> 00:16:36.230 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:16:35.000 --> 00:16:36.260 line:80%
Buy meat. Go. Go buy it.

00:16:36.310 --> 00:16:37.280 line:80%
Come on. Come on.

00:16:36.380 --> 00:16:39.980 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:16:37.310 --> 00:16:38.350 line:80%
-Come on.
-Buy some meat.

00:16:38.350 --> 00:16:38.950 line:80%
Come on.

00:16:40.110 --> 00:16:42.320 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:16:43.190 --> 00:16:45.120 line:80%
Just a little short of three taels.

00:17:03.280 --> 00:17:04.240 line:80%
This meat is perfect for dumplings.

00:17:04.240 --> 00:17:06.100 line:80%
Come back next time if you like it.

00:17:08.590 --> 00:17:09.550 line:80%
Did you see that?

00:17:10.310 --> 00:17:11.550 line:80%
That woman...

00:17:12.110 --> 00:17:13.869 line:80%
can cast spells.

00:17:14.440 --> 00:17:15.680 line:80%
Are you jealous

00:17:15.680 --> 00:17:16.869 line:80%
or just envious?

00:17:16.869 --> 00:17:18.129 line:80%
You have such a sharp tongue.

00:17:18.129 --> 00:17:19.610 line:80%
Watch out for karma.

00:17:19.300 --> 00:17:22.360 line:80%
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop]

00:17:19.869 --> 00:17:21.070 line:80%
I neither steal nor rob.

00:17:21.070 --> 00:17:22.550 line:80%
Why would karma find me?

00:17:22.869 --> 00:17:24.480 line:80%
Keep an eye on your man.

00:17:24.480 --> 00:17:26.590 line:80%
Then you'd better
keep an eye on your stove.

00:17:26.590 --> 00:17:28.040 line:80%
Or it might get smashed.

00:17:32.680 --> 00:17:33.240 line:80%
Okay.

00:17:33.630 --> 00:17:34.870 line:80%
Come again next time.

00:17:35.510 --> 00:17:37.230 line:80%
Pork!

00:17:38.650 --> 00:17:40.520 line:80%
Pork!

00:17:42.630 --> 00:17:43.960 line:80%
You little brat!

00:17:44.530 --> 00:17:46.320 line:80%
I'll beat you to death!

00:17:46.680 --> 00:17:47.240 line:80%
Grandma!

00:17:47.240 --> 00:17:48.040 line:80%
Grandma, Grandma, Grandma.

00:17:48.040 --> 00:17:48.800 line:80%
Wait, why are you here?

00:17:48.800 --> 00:17:49.520 line:80%
-I'll kill you!
-Grandma! Grandma!

00:17:49.520 --> 00:17:50.720 line:80%
Why are you hitting me?

00:17:50.720 --> 00:17:51.310 line:80%
You...

00:17:51.870 --> 00:17:53.550 line:80%
You're collecting protection money again!

00:17:53.550 --> 00:17:55.390 line:80%
Why can't you change?

00:17:55.440 --> 00:17:56.390 line:80%
I'm not collecting protection money!

00:17:56.390 --> 00:17:58.000 line:80%
Ask them if you don't believe me!

00:17:58.000 --> 00:17:59.350 line:80%
What's that in your hand?

00:17:59.350 --> 00:18:00.760 line:80%
Isn't that money?

00:18:01.550 --> 00:18:02.910 line:80%
Come on, I... This is money.

00:18:02.910 --> 00:18:04.640 line:80%
But it's not protection money.

00:18:07.150 --> 00:18:09.390 line:80%
The Fans just lost their parents.

00:18:09.800 --> 00:18:12.130 line:80%
There are only two poor orphan girls left.

00:18:12.150 --> 00:18:14.440 line:80%
Don't do such a cruel thing.

00:18:14.830 --> 00:18:15.360 line:80%
Don't...

00:18:15.830 --> 00:18:17.160 line:80%
Don't do such...

00:18:17.200 --> 00:18:18.520 line:80%
-a cruel thing!
-Grandma, stop hitting me!

00:18:18.520 --> 00:18:20.250 line:80%
Do you even know the situation?

00:18:20.590 --> 00:18:22.760 line:80%
Stop hitting me, Grandma!

00:18:22.870 --> 00:18:23.630 line:80%
Grandma Jin.

00:18:24.520 --> 00:18:26.520 line:80%
He really didn't
take any protection money from me.

00:18:26.520 --> 00:18:27.960 line:80%
They're helping me sell pork.

00:18:27.960 --> 00:18:29.360 line:80%
This is an honest living.

00:18:35.840 --> 00:18:36.800 line:80%
Selling pork?

00:18:40.280 --> 00:18:41.200 line:80%
Really?

00:18:42.280 --> 00:18:43.060 line:80%
Really.

00:18:43.910 --> 00:18:45.370 line:80%
They swept this floor, too.

00:18:45.370 --> 00:18:46.170 line:80%
That's right.

00:18:46.390 --> 00:18:47.650 line:80%
And the stove outside—

00:18:47.820 --> 00:18:49.340 line:80%
they helped fix it, too.

00:18:51.800 --> 00:18:53.330 line:80%
Everyone saw it, right?

00:18:54.720 --> 00:18:56.100 line:80%
I guess so.

00:19:03.530 --> 00:19:04.730 line:80%
My grandson...

00:19:04.960 --> 00:19:05.910 line:80%
has grown up.

00:19:07.800 --> 00:19:10.950 line:80%
My grandson used to be a good kid.

00:19:13.720 --> 00:19:16.900 line:80%
Work hard and honestly from now on.

00:19:17.150 --> 00:19:19.440 line:80%
Don't hold up Mrs. Fan's business.

00:19:19.520 --> 00:19:21.350 line:80%
Grandma, just go home.

00:19:21.350 --> 00:19:23.000 line:80%
You're holding up our business now, okay?

00:19:23.000 --> 00:19:24.680 line:80%
-Alright, alright.
-Hurry up and go.

00:19:24.680 --> 00:19:25.310 line:80%
Alright.

00:19:26.350 --> 00:19:26.910 line:80%
I...

00:19:30.960 --> 00:19:32.540 line:80%
Look at you.

00:19:32.830 --> 00:19:34.000 line:80%
Work hard.

00:19:41.760 --> 00:19:43.790 line:80%
My grandson has grown up.

00:19:44.480 --> 00:19:47.040 line:80%
He won't do bad things anymore.

00:19:55.040 --> 00:19:56.100 line:80%
Alright, alright.

00:20:00.150 --> 00:20:01.760 line:80%
My grandma, honestly.

00:20:01.800 --> 00:20:02.630 line:80%
I mean, look how old I am.

00:20:02.630 --> 00:20:04.360 line:80%
She still treats me like a baby.

00:20:04.390 --> 00:20:07.720 line:80%
If word gets out, how am I supposed to
survive on the streets?

00:20:08.410 --> 00:20:10.520 line:80%
Stop staring.
If you want to buy meat, hurry up.

00:20:10.520 --> 00:20:11.650 line:80%
If not, get lost.

00:20:13.680 --> 00:20:14.550 line:80%
Have a taste.

00:20:15.070 --> 00:20:17.350 line:80%
You still have family in this world
who treats you so well.

00:20:17.350 --> 00:20:18.610 line:80%
You should be content.

00:20:18.760 --> 00:20:20.070 line:80%
You have hands and feet.

00:20:20.070 --> 00:20:21.720 line:80%
Why not do some honest work?

00:20:23.200 --> 00:20:25.440 line:80%
But I don't know any honest work to do.

00:20:26.830 --> 00:20:28.000 line:80%
In a time like this,

00:20:28.680 --> 00:20:31.590 line:80%
it's hard to be a bad guy,
but even harder to be a good one.

00:20:31.590 --> 00:20:32.550 line:80%
Manwu's mother

00:20:32.910 --> 00:20:35.310 line:80%
has been sick for years
and needs medicine.

00:20:35.960 --> 00:20:37.290 line:80%
Mandi's younger sister

00:20:37.330 --> 00:20:39.680 line:80%
was sent by her uncle
to do chores at a brothel.

00:20:39.680 --> 00:20:41.040 line:80%
She's 6 months away from coming of age.

00:20:41.040 --> 00:20:42.320 line:80%
If she isn't redeemed by then,

00:20:42.320 --> 00:20:44.380 line:80%
she'll be forced into prostitution.

00:20:48.740 --> 00:20:49.430 line:80%
Mancang...

00:20:50.720 --> 00:20:52.310 line:80%
has been an orphan since childhood.

00:20:52.310 --> 00:20:53.960 line:80%
He eats a lot but has no brains.

00:20:53.960 --> 00:20:56.160 line:80%
He can't do any work. Who would want him?

00:20:57.760 --> 00:20:59.360 line:80%
We want to be good people too,

00:21:00.040 --> 00:21:01.900 line:80%
but in these years of endless war,

00:21:02.980 --> 00:21:04.510 line:80%
good people can't survive.

00:21:12.150 --> 00:21:13.440 line:80%
This meat is half fat and half lean.

00:21:13.440 --> 00:21:14.760 line:80%
It's perfect for making dumplings.

00:21:14.760 --> 00:21:16.000 line:80%
We charge 35 per jin.

00:21:16.030 --> 00:21:17.520 line:80%
It's a little over two jin.

00:21:17.520 --> 00:21:19.200 line:80%
I'll just count it as 2 jin for you,
alright?

00:21:19.200 --> 00:21:19.760 line:80%
Sure.

00:21:19.910 --> 00:21:20.870 line:80%
Let me weigh it for you.

00:21:20.870 --> 00:21:21.800 line:80%
I have more here.

00:21:22.550 --> 00:21:23.810 line:80%
Take care. Come again.

00:21:24.520 --> 00:21:25.910 line:80%
Pork!

00:22:08.520 --> 00:22:10.580 line:80%
Eat up. This is a meal for good people.

00:22:10.830 --> 00:22:11.890 line:80%
It's not poisoned.

00:22:35.680 --> 00:22:36.940 line:80%
This is today's wages.

00:22:37.070 --> 00:22:38.310 line:80%
You only worked half a day,

00:22:38.310 --> 00:22:40.040 line:80%
so you only get half a day's pay.

00:22:40.110 --> 00:22:41.170 line:80%
I won't give extra,

00:22:41.870 --> 00:22:43.870 line:80%
but I won't owe you anything either.

00:22:54.310 --> 00:22:56.570 line:80%
Slow down. You eat like starving ghosts.

00:22:59.910 --> 00:23:00.720 line:80%
Mrs. Fan.

00:23:06.590 --> 00:23:07.390 line:80%
Um...

00:23:08.040 --> 00:23:10.240 line:80%
Can we come help in the future?

00:23:16.070 --> 00:23:17.110 line:80%
If you need food

00:23:17.240 --> 00:23:19.040 line:80%
and want to work, you're welcome.

00:23:19.040 --> 00:23:20.090 line:80%
But if you do anything bad,

00:23:20.090 --> 00:23:21.090 line:80%
I won't be polite.

00:23:36.590 --> 00:23:38.650 line:80%
It's Wang's on Middle Street, right?

00:23:39.440 --> 00:23:40.070 line:80%
Yes.

00:23:43.350 --> 00:23:44.810 line:80%
Are you going for revenge?

00:23:45.470 --> 00:23:46.390 line:80%
Mrs. Yin!

00:23:46.800 --> 00:23:48.960 line:80%
Keep an eye on the shop for me. Thanks.

00:23:46.890 --> 00:23:48.900 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:23:51.040 --> 00:23:51.720 line:80%
Okay!

00:23:59.320 --> 00:24:00.850 line:80%
We can't be disloyal.

00:24:00.920 --> 00:24:01.740 line:80%
Follow her.

00:24:06.960 --> 00:24:09.390 line:80%
No wonder those hooligans listen to her.

00:24:10.590 --> 00:24:12.410 line:80%
She's the boss of them!

00:24:13.800 --> 00:24:14.550 line:80%
Sir,

00:24:14.870 --> 00:24:16.000 line:80%
this much money...

00:24:16.020 --> 00:24:19.040 line:80%
if you spend it all on rice, flour,
salt, oil, sauce, and vinegar,

00:24:19.040 --> 00:24:20.670 line:80%
one cart won't hold it all.

00:24:20.910 --> 00:24:22.170 line:80%
Then add another cart.

00:24:22.830 --> 00:24:23.760 line:80%
Alright.

00:24:23.670 --> 00:24:26.370 line:80%
[Fan Erniu's residence
on the east section of Xigu Lane]

00:24:23.990 --> 00:24:25.480 line:80%
Add 10 more jars of good wine,

00:24:25.480 --> 00:24:27.410 line:80%
the kind suitable for the elderly.

00:24:27.480 --> 00:24:29.070 line:80%
Also some tea and pastries.

00:24:29.200 --> 00:24:30.200 line:80%
Send them to this address.

00:24:30.200 --> 00:24:31.040 line:80%
No problem.

00:24:34.720 --> 00:24:35.320 line:80%
By the way,

00:24:35.910 --> 00:24:38.720 line:80%
do you have any ointment for chapped skin?

00:24:39.040 --> 00:24:40.000 line:80%
Yes, we do.

00:24:41.480 --> 00:24:43.870 line:80%
We have the best clam oil.

00:24:45.800 --> 00:24:47.910 line:80%
Newly arrived. Take a look.

00:24:52.620 --> 00:24:53.680 line:80%
I'll take them all.

00:24:55.400 --> 00:24:56.270 line:80%
Okay, sir.

00:24:59.070 --> 00:25:01.390 line:80%
Where did you get your wrist guards?

00:25:02.520 --> 00:25:04.520 line:80%
Do they have ones suitable for ladies?

00:25:04.520 --> 00:25:05.850 line:80%
Sir, you must be joking.

00:25:06.390 --> 00:25:07.440 line:80%
Men

00:25:07.550 --> 00:25:09.280 line:80%
use these

00:25:09.520 --> 00:25:10.800 line:80%
for hard labor.

00:25:11.000 --> 00:25:12.870 line:80%
Why would a girl need them?

00:25:13.440 --> 00:25:15.100 line:80%
You can't find them anywhere.

00:25:17.070 --> 00:25:18.890 line:80%
Where's Mrs. Fan going?

00:25:19.350 --> 00:25:20.630 line:80%
She looks furious.

00:25:21.520 --> 00:25:23.320 line:80%
I heard she's going for revenge.

00:25:26.630 --> 00:25:27.710 line:80%
What's going on?

00:25:27.760 --> 00:25:28.830 line:80%
Haven't you heard?

00:25:28.830 --> 00:25:30.800 line:80%
Wang's Braised Meat Shop
was jealous of her business

00:25:30.800 --> 00:25:33.230 line:80%
and sent people to smash Fan's shop.

00:25:33.440 --> 00:25:36.370 line:80%
See? Fan's sent people
to retaliate against Wang's.

00:25:37.000 --> 00:25:37.960 line:80%
If anyone asks,

00:25:38.040 --> 00:25:40.310 line:80%
just say Fan Erniu deposited money
in your shop

00:25:40.310 --> 00:25:43.040 line:80%
to be exchanged for New Year's goods
before the holiday.

00:25:43.040 --> 00:25:43.840 line:80%
Alright, sir.

00:25:45.310 --> 00:25:46.550 line:80%
Such a fine young lady,

00:25:46.550 --> 00:25:48.000 line:80%
acting like a thug.

00:25:48.000 --> 00:25:49.200 line:80%
Don't you agree, sir?

00:25:50.000 --> 00:25:51.610 line:80%
Thank you. Thank you.

00:25:57.830 --> 00:25:59.260 line:80%
Mrs. Fan, are you here to...

00:25:57.910 --> 00:25:58.370 line:80%
[Wang's Braised Meat Shop]

00:26:00.240 --> 00:26:01.240 line:80%
Gentlemen...

00:26:00.300 --> 00:26:02.750 line:80%
[Wang's Braised Meat Shop]

00:26:01.240 --> 00:26:02.240 line:80%
Move!

00:26:04.240 --> 00:26:05.960 line:80%
Tell your shopkeeper to come out.

00:26:05.960 --> 00:26:07.680 line:80%
He had the guts to smash my shop,

00:26:07.680 --> 00:26:09.610 line:80%
but now he's hiding like a coward?

00:26:10.040 --> 00:26:11.240 line:80%
What's going on here?

00:26:11.680 --> 00:26:12.590 line:80%
Gentlemen,

00:26:12.720 --> 00:26:13.350 line:80%
let's wait for our shopkeeper

00:26:13.350 --> 00:26:15.000 line:80%
before we discuss anything.

00:26:15.040 --> 00:26:17.310 line:80%
What's all the noise?

00:26:20.110 --> 00:26:20.910 line:80%
Young Master.

00:26:29.500 --> 00:26:31.590 line:80%
It was you who sent men to smash my shop?

00:26:31.590 --> 00:26:34.000 line:80%
It was him. He gave us 5 taels of silver

00:26:34.000 --> 00:26:35.550 line:80%
for smashing your stove.

00:26:36.200 --> 00:26:37.240 line:80%
Who are you?

00:26:37.350 --> 00:26:39.430 line:80%
Trying to deny it?

00:26:39.450 --> 00:26:41.680 line:80%
We were drinking at the tavern

00:26:41.720 --> 00:26:43.370 line:80%
when you approached us.

00:26:43.400 --> 00:26:44.200 line:80%
You're still trying to deny it?

00:26:44.200 --> 00:26:44.910 line:80%
Exactly.

00:26:45.000 --> 00:26:46.630 line:80%
The tavern owner can testify too.

00:26:46.630 --> 00:26:48.920 line:80%
Whoever denies it is a coward.

00:26:48.950 --> 00:26:50.580 line:80%
The Young Master of Wang's,

00:26:50.720 --> 00:26:52.150 line:80%
daring to smash my stove

00:26:52.150 --> 00:26:53.410 line:80%
but afraid to admit it?

00:27:00.030 --> 00:27:01.900 line:80%
It was just a stove.

00:27:02.910 --> 00:27:04.280 line:80%
So what if I smashed it?

00:27:05.350 --> 00:27:06.480 line:80%
What can you do to me?

00:27:08.590 --> 00:27:10.450 line:80%
You're a girl.

00:27:11.110 --> 00:27:13.350 line:80%
Instead of staying in your room
doing embroidery,

00:27:13.350 --> 00:27:15.720 line:80%
you're out here trying to do business.

00:27:16.240 --> 00:27:18.770 line:80%
Aren't you just asking
to be a laughingstock?

00:27:21.930 --> 00:27:23.410 line:80%
Just because I'm a girl,

00:27:24.330 --> 00:27:25.990 line:80%
I deserve to be bullied by you?

00:27:27.200 --> 00:27:28.720 line:80%
I'm not bullying you.

00:27:29.310 --> 00:27:31.690 line:80%
I feel sorry for you.

00:27:33.590 --> 00:27:34.390 line:80%
Look at you.

00:27:35.390 --> 00:27:37.350 line:80%
You're quite pretty.

00:27:37.800 --> 00:27:41.590 line:80%
Why suffer for such a small business?

00:27:44.250 --> 00:27:45.890 line:80%
I have plenty of money.

00:27:50.150 --> 00:27:50.880 line:80%
Name a price.

00:27:52.040 --> 00:27:55.840 line:80%
Sell me the recipe and yourself.
How about it?

00:28:01.270 --> 00:28:03.130 line:80%
Who the hell do you think you are?

00:28:03.770 --> 00:28:05.830 line:80%
You think you're worthy of my recipe?

00:28:10.670 --> 00:28:11.990 line:80%
You bitch.

00:28:12.880 --> 00:28:16.650 line:80%
You slept with that old Cook Li

00:28:16.830 --> 00:28:19.480 line:80%
to cut off our business
with Yixiang Restaurant.

00:28:19.480 --> 00:28:21.310 line:80%
And now you dared to come here?

00:28:21.310 --> 00:28:22.520 line:80%
You butcher girl.

00:28:22.520 --> 00:28:24.120 line:80%
How can you be so...

00:28:31.000 --> 00:28:32.550 line:80%
Bravo! Bravo!

00:28:34.900 --> 00:28:37.110 line:80%
When she beat us up earlier,

00:28:37.680 --> 00:28:39.410 line:80%
she was actually holding back?

00:28:41.150 --> 00:28:41.910 line:80%
Tell me.

00:28:43.070 --> 00:28:46.130 line:80%
How did I steal your business
with Yixiang Restaurant?

00:28:46.680 --> 00:28:51.160 line:80%
I-I heard that Wang's lost the business
with Yixiang Restaurant

00:28:51.440 --> 00:28:54.930 line:80%
because Chef Li recommended your meat.

00:28:56.240 --> 00:28:57.300 line:80%
So because of that,

00:28:57.550 --> 00:28:59.480 line:80%
you're spreading rumors about me?

00:28:59.980 --> 00:29:00.870 line:80%
I was wrong.

00:29:01.350 --> 00:29:02.240 line:80%
You taught him a good lesson!

00:29:02.240 --> 00:29:02.960 line:80%
Yes!

00:29:02.960 --> 00:29:05.070 line:80%
It's lucky she's Fan Erniu's daughter.

00:29:05.070 --> 00:29:06.720 line:80%
If it were another girl,

00:29:06.720 --> 00:29:08.180 line:80%
being bullied like this,

00:29:08.330 --> 00:29:09.640 line:80%
she would have no way...

00:29:09.640 --> 00:29:10.960 line:80%
To deal with it.

00:29:10.960 --> 00:29:12.150 line:80%
That's right.

00:29:12.150 --> 00:29:13.310 line:80%
In my opinion,

00:29:13.310 --> 00:29:15.150 line:80%
Wang's shop bullies customers
because it's big.

00:29:15.150 --> 00:29:16.000 line:80%
Exactly.

00:29:16.110 --> 00:29:18.070 line:80%
Back when the old man was around,

00:29:18.070 --> 00:29:19.800 line:80%
their business was booming.

00:29:19.820 --> 00:29:22.010 line:80%
Ever since Old Wang passed away,

00:29:22.040 --> 00:29:24.120 line:80%
their braised meat
has gotten worse day by day.

00:29:24.120 --> 00:29:25.390 line:80%
-Right?
-Yes!

00:29:25.610 --> 00:29:26.520 line:80%
No wonder Yixiang Restaurant

00:29:26.520 --> 00:29:27.910 line:80%
stopped doing business with him.

00:29:27.910 --> 00:29:28.710 line:80%
Serves him right!

00:29:28.710 --> 00:29:31.640 line:80%
If it were me,
I wouldn't do business with him either.

00:29:32.210 --> 00:29:34.500 line:80%
If you dare to spread rumors

00:29:34.550 --> 00:29:36.520 line:80%
and ruin a woman's reputation again,

00:29:36.520 --> 00:29:38.060 line:80%
be careful—

00:29:40.590 --> 00:29:42.250 line:80%
this knife of mine has no eyes.

00:29:42.650 --> 00:29:43.720 line:80%
Got it.

00:29:56.550 --> 00:29:58.230 line:80%
-You bastard!
-Young Master!

00:29:59.480 --> 00:30:01.040 line:80%
Today, I…

00:30:01.980 --> 00:30:03.740 line:80%
[Wang's Braised Meat Shop]

00:30:04.520 --> 00:30:07.150 line:80%
[Liuji Sugar Shop]

00:30:07.250 --> 00:30:09.830 line:80%
[Wang's Braised Meat Shop]

00:30:13.040 --> 00:30:14.040 line:80%
Let me see you off.

00:30:15.020 --> 00:30:19.110 line:80%
[Liuji Sugar Shop]

00:30:26.630 --> 00:30:28.630 line:80%
That's Changyu from the Fan family?

00:30:30.310 --> 00:30:31.150 line:80%
Exactly.

00:30:33.690 --> 00:30:34.490 line:80%
Interesting.

00:30:35.020 --> 00:30:37.480 line:80%
I didn't expect her to be so rough,
like a man.

00:30:38.680 --> 00:30:39.350 line:80%
Let's go.

00:30:40.280 --> 00:30:40.870 line:80%
Let's go.

00:30:49.910 --> 00:30:51.110 line:80%
Your injury hasn't fully healed yet.

00:30:51.110 --> 00:30:52.440 line:80%
Why did you come to town?

00:30:53.440 --> 00:30:54.770 line:80%
Just came to have a look.

00:30:55.000 --> 00:30:56.460 line:80%
I heard you went to Wang's,

00:30:56.630 --> 00:30:57.910 line:80%
so I came to pick you up.

00:30:58.590 --> 00:30:59.520 line:80%
How did it go?

00:31:00.310 --> 00:31:02.240 line:80%
I hadn't even started hitting anyone yet.

00:31:02.240 --> 00:31:03.720 line:80%
I just kicked his table,

00:31:03.840 --> 00:31:05.300 line:80%
and he was scared to death.

00:31:05.310 --> 00:31:06.000 line:80%
Then he...

00:31:08.760 --> 00:31:10.160 line:80%
Why did you stop talking?

00:31:11.240 --> 00:31:11.960 line:80%
Do you...

00:31:12.310 --> 00:31:14.710 line:80%
think I'm vulgar too?

00:31:17.550 --> 00:31:19.100 line:80%
You bastard!

00:31:33.390 --> 00:31:34.820 line:80%
Only those with enough to eat
and a roof over their heads

00:31:34.820 --> 00:31:36.350 line:80%
worry whether their actions

00:31:36.250 --> 00:31:38.450 line:80%
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

00:31:36.350 --> 00:31:37.690 line:80%
are crude or refined.

00:31:38.240 --> 00:31:40.040 line:80%
For people who spend all their energy
just to survive,

00:31:39.520 --> 00:31:40.490 line:80%
♪ With very pale colors ♪

00:31:40.490 --> 00:31:42.360 line:80%
no one has the right to judge them.

00:31:41.520 --> 00:31:44.360 line:80%
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

00:31:44.940 --> 00:31:47.280 line:80%
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

00:31:47.310 --> 00:31:49.830 line:80%
In the past, my father wouldn't let me
use force in front of outsiders.

00:31:48.180 --> 00:31:49.500 line:80%
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

00:31:50.340 --> 00:31:54.500 line:80%
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

00:31:51.200 --> 00:31:52.800 line:80%
My mother was even stricter.

00:31:53.110 --> 00:31:55.240 line:80%
She wouldn't even let me butcher pigs.

00:31:55.310 --> 00:31:57.390 line:80%
She said if a girl knows
how to do these things,

00:31:57.390 --> 00:31:58.440 line:80%
people would gossip,

00:31:57.870 --> 00:32:00.340 line:80%
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

00:32:00.350 --> 00:32:02.240 line:80%
and that if I marry Song Yan
in the future,

00:32:01.140 --> 00:32:02.750 line:80%
♪ The light shines ♪

00:32:02.240 --> 00:32:03.530 line:80%
even if he doesn't mind,

00:32:03.440 --> 00:32:06.180 line:80%
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

00:32:04.350 --> 00:32:06.610 line:80%
others will still gossip behind my back.

00:32:06.630 --> 00:32:09.240 line:80%
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

00:32:08.070 --> 00:32:09.400 line:80%
Later, my parents died.

00:32:09.860 --> 00:32:11.600 line:80%
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

00:32:10.720 --> 00:32:11.900 line:80%
To make a living,

00:32:12.050 --> 00:32:16.930 line:80%
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

00:32:12.550 --> 00:32:15.010 line:80%
I had no choice
but to start butchering pigs.

00:32:15.220 --> 00:32:17.960 line:80%
I even used a stick
to teach people a lesson a few times.

00:32:17.960 --> 00:32:19.150 line:80%
Now, people in town

00:32:19.150 --> 00:32:21.050 line:80%
probably all think I'm a she-devil.

00:32:19.460 --> 00:32:20.530 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love ♪

00:32:20.560 --> 00:32:23.250 line:80%
♪ Will never end ♪

00:32:22.570 --> 00:32:24.730 line:80%
A gambling house even sent me an offer,

00:32:23.920 --> 00:32:24.800 line:80%
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

00:32:24.820 --> 00:32:27.200 line:80%
♪ For a lifetime ♪

00:32:25.310 --> 00:32:27.590 line:80%
saying if I don't butcher pigs
in the future,

00:32:27.590 --> 00:32:28.870 line:80%
I can go help them collect debts.

00:32:27.830 --> 00:32:31.920 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:32:30.830 --> 00:32:32.090 line:80%
Then go collect debts.

00:32:32.390 --> 00:32:35.760 line:80%
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

00:32:33.070 --> 00:32:33.760 line:80%
Really?

00:32:35.150 --> 00:32:36.860 line:80%
You're encouraging me to do that?

00:32:36.770 --> 00:32:37.700 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love
will not be like sand ♪

00:32:37.040 --> 00:32:39.120 line:80%
I'm telling you
not to fear people's words.

00:32:37.720 --> 00:32:40.180 line:80%
♪ Slipping into the sea ♪

00:32:40.480 --> 00:32:42.000 line:80%
Spreading rumors and slandering

00:32:41.510 --> 00:32:42.450 line:80%
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

00:32:42.110 --> 00:32:43.480 line:80%
costs nothing

00:32:42.470 --> 00:32:44.910 line:80%
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

00:32:43.910 --> 00:32:45.440 line:80%
but causes great harm,

00:32:45.480 --> 00:32:46.830 line:80%
especially to women.

00:32:45.620 --> 00:32:49.510 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:32:47.150 --> 00:32:48.610 line:80%
You have to make them hurt,

00:32:49.040 --> 00:32:50.580 line:80%
hurt more than the victim,

00:32:49.990 --> 00:32:58.180 line:80%
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

00:32:51.040 --> 00:32:52.350 line:80%
to set things right.

00:32:55.700 --> 00:32:57.620 line:80%
Set things right?

00:32:57.800 --> 00:32:59.470 line:80%
What does that mean?

00:33:03.150 --> 00:33:03.830 line:80%
Guess.

00:33:03.290 --> 00:33:07.660 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet ♪

00:33:04.830 --> 00:33:05.680 line:80%
I don't know.

00:33:06.830 --> 00:33:07.550 line:80%
Guess again.

00:33:07.550 --> 00:33:08.680 line:80%
So what does it mean?

00:33:09.310 --> 00:33:11.370 line:80%
Basically, it means...

00:33:09.570 --> 00:33:15.580 line:80%
♪ As me ♪

00:33:20.630 --> 00:33:22.550 line:80%
Changyu, eat. Zheng, eat.

00:33:25.000 --> 00:33:26.270 line:80%
Where did this oil...

00:33:26.630 --> 00:33:29.040 line:80%
and all these things come from?

00:33:29.110 --> 00:33:30.680 line:80%
Father bought them.

00:33:31.280 --> 00:33:32.480 line:80%
Don't talk nonsense.

00:33:33.110 --> 00:33:35.110 line:80%
Changning isn't talking nonsense.

00:33:35.200 --> 00:33:37.440 line:80%
I was confused seeing so many things too.

00:33:37.440 --> 00:33:40.760 line:80%
The clerk said your father saved the money
at their place months ago

00:33:40.760 --> 00:33:43.110 line:80%
to exchange it all for New Year goods,
which would be delivered here.

00:33:43.110 --> 00:33:45.170 line:80%
Where did my father get so much money?

00:33:47.070 --> 00:33:48.520 line:80%
Was it really my father?

00:33:48.590 --> 00:33:50.630 line:80%
Yes, someone named Fan Erniu.

00:33:50.630 --> 00:33:52.480 line:80%
See? It can't be fake.

00:33:53.110 --> 00:33:53.760 line:80%
Who in these days

00:33:53.760 --> 00:33:57.490 line:80%
would be foolish enough to deliver goods
for someone else for free?

00:33:58.280 --> 00:33:59.810 line:80%
Yan Zheng, don't you agree?

00:34:00.960 --> 00:34:01.550 line:80%
Yes.

00:34:02.950 --> 00:34:05.100 line:80%
Besides, just this amount of stuff

00:34:05.240 --> 00:34:06.700 line:80%
isn't that unusual, is it?

00:34:09.880 --> 00:34:11.380 line:80%
Just?

00:34:12.990 --> 00:34:15.410 line:80%
Changyu, look. There's also this.

00:34:18.560 --> 00:34:19.720 line:80%
Clam oil?

00:34:19.830 --> 00:34:21.170 line:80%
The food is fine,

00:34:21.350 --> 00:34:23.410 line:80%
but why did he buy this useless stuff?

00:34:23.720 --> 00:34:24.800 line:80%
Which shop is it from?

00:34:24.800 --> 00:34:25.660 line:80%
I'll return it.

00:34:25.830 --> 00:34:26.830 line:80%
Don't return it.

00:34:27.430 --> 00:34:29.910 line:80%
Father must have felt sorry
for your chapped hands

00:34:29.910 --> 00:34:31.439 line:80%
and prepared it for you.

00:34:31.510 --> 00:34:33.300 line:80%
Our father wouldn't be so silly

00:34:33.330 --> 00:34:34.860 line:80%
to buy such useless things.

00:34:35.200 --> 00:34:36.760 line:80%
I'll return it and buy you candy.

00:34:36.760 --> 00:34:37.430 line:80%
Wait.

00:34:43.030 --> 00:34:44.030 line:80%
Once you use it...

00:34:45.720 --> 00:34:47.010 line:80%
you can't return it.

00:34:51.720 --> 00:34:53.310 line:80%
If you like it, take it and use it.

00:34:53.310 --> 00:34:54.170 line:80%
I don't like it.

00:34:54.350 --> 00:34:56.160 line:80%
Then why did you use it?

00:34:57.760 --> 00:35:00.020 line:80%
Now that it's used, it can't be returned.

00:35:01.380 --> 00:35:04.730 line:80%
Silly girl, your husband cares about you

00:35:04.830 --> 00:35:06.890 line:80%
and wants you to keep it for yourself.

00:35:44.280 --> 00:35:45.680 line:80%
Since it's already used,

00:35:46.960 --> 00:35:48.740 line:80%
I'll just use it.

00:35:58.830 --> 00:36:00.490 line:80%
Buying these useless things,

00:36:01.670 --> 00:36:03.600 line:80%
I wonder what Father was thinking.

00:36:06.080 --> 00:36:07.030 line:80%
Your father

00:36:07.880 --> 00:36:09.410 line:80%
was thinking exactly that.

00:36:30.390 --> 00:36:31.280 line:80%
Tomorrow,

00:36:32.230 --> 00:36:33.960 line:80%
the court will begin the trial.

00:36:34.990 --> 00:36:36.590 line:80%
Do you need me to go with you?

00:36:37.760 --> 00:36:38.430 line:80%
No need.

00:36:38.910 --> 00:36:40.520 line:80%
Mr. Zhao and the others will be with me.

00:36:40.520 --> 00:36:41.720 line:80%
You have a leg injury,

00:36:41.750 --> 00:36:43.280 line:80%
so you can't kneel for long.

00:36:45.280 --> 00:36:47.240 line:80%
I've remembered everything you taught me.

00:36:47.240 --> 00:36:48.100 line:80%
I'm not afraid.

00:36:57.990 --> 00:36:59.790 line:80%
Knives are not allowed in court.

00:37:02.720 --> 00:37:03.990 line:80%
This is my livelihood.

00:37:03.990 --> 00:37:05.590 line:80%
Forbidden means forbidden!

00:37:14.870 --> 00:37:17.780 line:80%
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

00:37:22.830 --> 00:37:24.690 line:80%
[Government]

00:37:29.460 --> 00:37:32.070 line:80%
Why haven't I seen Fan Daniu and his wife?

00:37:32.870 --> 00:37:34.270 line:80%
Did they forget the time?

00:37:36.760 --> 00:37:38.440 line:80%
Those two heartless people.

00:37:38.800 --> 00:37:41.120 line:80%
I'd believe it
if they forgot their parents' names.

00:37:41.120 --> 00:37:42.600 line:80%
But forgetting about fighting for a house?

00:37:42.600 --> 00:37:44.000 line:80%
I don't think they would.

00:37:44.830 --> 00:37:45.470 line:80%
True.

00:37:46.640 --> 00:37:48.080 line:80%
Then where did they go?

00:37:49.080 --> 00:37:50.480 line:80%
They are the plaintiffs.

00:37:58.800 --> 00:38:03.520 line:80%
[Righteousness]

00:38:02.280 --> 00:38:03.030 line:80%
Start the trial.

00:38:03.030 --> 00:38:06.430 line:80%
Beware!

00:38:06.800 --> 00:38:09.800 line:80%
Bring the plaintiffs
and the defendants to the court.

00:38:10.290 --> 00:38:12.460 line:80%
[Government]

00:38:16.970 --> 00:38:18.750 line:80%
Who is kneeling down there?

00:38:18.990 --> 00:38:20.590 line:80%
I am Fan Changyu.

00:38:20.680 --> 00:38:22.600 line:80%
Greetings, Your Honor!

00:38:29.790 --> 00:38:32.350 line:80%
[Righteousness]

00:38:30.200 --> 00:38:32.430 line:80%
Where is the plaintiff, Fan Daniu?

00:38:40.470 --> 00:38:41.560 line:80%
Preposterous!

00:38:42.200 --> 00:38:43.990 line:80%
I have been a judge for so long,

00:38:44.350 --> 00:38:48.010 line:80%
but this is the first time
I've seen a plaintiff absent from court.

00:38:49.950 --> 00:38:51.160 line:80%
Please calm down, My Lord.

00:38:51.160 --> 00:38:52.910 line:80%
Fan Daniu must have a reason

00:38:52.910 --> 00:38:54.350 line:80%
for being late.

00:38:54.470 --> 00:38:57.130 line:80%
Why not send a police runner
to his home to check?

00:38:57.310 --> 00:39:00.440 line:80%
This will show your fairness
and impartiality, My Lord.

00:39:01.310 --> 00:39:01.950 line:80%
Granted.

00:39:03.030 --> 00:39:04.290 line:80%
Well, Constable Wang,

00:39:04.390 --> 00:39:06.990 line:80%
send someone
to the Fan family in East Village.

00:39:07.240 --> 00:39:07.800 line:80%
Yes.

00:39:08.830 --> 00:39:11.160 line:80%
Court is adjourned for now.

00:39:11.600 --> 00:39:12.160 line:80%
Dismiss.

00:39:12.760 --> 00:39:13.760 line:80%
It's dismissed just like that?

00:39:13.760 --> 00:39:14.420 line:80%
Yeah.

00:39:15.280 --> 00:39:16.030 line:80%
Come on. Make way.

00:39:16.030 --> 00:39:17.600 line:80%
Wang, what's going on?

00:39:17.950 --> 00:39:18.750 line:80%
It's nothing.

00:39:18.870 --> 00:39:19.350 line:80%
Come.

00:39:24.160 --> 00:39:26.930 line:80%
Did Changyu catch Fan Daniu?

00:39:27.080 --> 00:39:28.430 line:80%
Why would she catch him?

00:39:28.830 --> 00:39:30.830 line:80%
Changyu is already married.

00:39:30.830 --> 00:39:34.030 line:80%
It's an obviously winning lawsuit.
That wouldn't be necessary.

00:39:34.030 --> 00:39:34.560 line:80%
Besides,

00:39:34.560 --> 00:39:36.670 line:80%
she stayed at home all last night.

00:39:37.030 --> 00:39:38.600 line:80%
Okay. I'm relieved then.

00:39:41.940 --> 00:39:45.060 line:80%
[Government]

00:39:45.170 --> 00:39:48.230 line:80%
[Righteousness]

00:39:48.330 --> 00:39:51.610 line:80%
[Qingping County Government Office]

00:39:51.710 --> 00:39:55.530 line:80%
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

00:40:02.280 --> 00:40:03.210 line:80%
Start the trial.

00:40:03.230 --> 00:40:07.060 line:80%
Beware!

00:40:07.390 --> 00:40:10.020 line:80%
Your Honor,
I have a matrilocal husband now.

00:40:10.040 --> 00:40:13.040 line:80%
According to the law,
I can inherit the family estate.

00:40:15.870 --> 00:40:17.390 line:80%
We have waited for 2 hours.

00:40:17.600 --> 00:40:19.000 line:80%
We won't wait any longer.

00:40:19.030 --> 00:40:21.090 line:80%
Since the plaintiff has not arrived,

00:40:21.280 --> 00:40:23.030 line:80%
I now pronounce

00:40:23.200 --> 00:40:25.060 line:80%
that the defendant wins the case!

00:40:25.720 --> 00:40:27.080 line:80%
My Lord!

00:40:28.800 --> 00:40:29.870 line:80%
My Lord!

00:40:30.640 --> 00:40:31.800 line:80%
My Lord!

00:40:35.600 --> 00:40:40.200 line:80%
You must seek justice for me, My Lord!

00:40:44.680 --> 00:40:45.600 line:80%
My Lord,

00:40:46.470 --> 00:40:49.560 line:80%
you must seek justice for me!

00:40:59.470 --> 00:41:01.200 line:80%
You jinx!

00:41:01.950 --> 00:41:03.680 line:80%
To steal this house,

00:41:03.800 --> 00:41:06.470 line:80%
you actually killed your uncle!